Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.92,0:01:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静谧天地之间  以栖宿其中之脉动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.14,0:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倾听奏鸣之心音  格守秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.78,0:02:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝将成青色大义之卫士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.25,0:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誓言挥剑时将心怀佩剑者的尊严与信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接过这把剑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.65,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一位王说  握住我的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.54,0:02:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二位王说  握住我的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是少年们和王相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.27,0:03:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏进了“另一边”的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  真无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.66,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才讨厌这种贵族学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个个都那么不识趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.47,0:03:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁间在做什么  现在不是上课时间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也在玩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.69,0:04:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是伏见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  吓到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你也没在如厕  应该没关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么没去上课啊  伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是伏见猿比古吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是八田啊  跟你同班的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚远点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是Jungle的SNS吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近还挺流行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.39,0:04:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天才听人介绍  刚加入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.73,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不清楚怎么操作呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会打扰你  能听我说话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见你常玩Jungle吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.97,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天加入Jungle以后  手机就一直收到奇怪的短信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见你也有收到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.53,0:05:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你也玩钓鱼游戏的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看就过来看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以过来看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你能用正常方法进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.64,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在跟人对战吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Jungle里一个叫Jcube的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.18,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才上钩的对手  是我们学校的初三的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你被打啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.74,0:06:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三年几班的？我帮你修理他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害  你太厉害了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.27,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是又好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.69,0:06:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早啊  伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么东西  挑战书吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.51,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣  要是欠揍就来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田美咲同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.73,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚要不要一起去看夜景呢  阿耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这 这 这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等 等 等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是鸡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这 这… 你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛  别把垃圾丢给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才不是垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是放在鞋柜里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.30,0:08:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是倒楣信件吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.59,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦  这你都看不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.72,0:08:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人都知道这是情书吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.35,0:08:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲咲  你好清纯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.92,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫大贝阿耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大贝..阿耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿耶的信你看了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你  你的信？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能陪我一起去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  我今天跟伏见约好打游戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.81,0:09:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别见死不救啊  伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.99,0:09:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你Jcube的排名为什么掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厌了所以就不玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怕输给阿耶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了就落跑真是太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.13,0:10:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  原来你们认识啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.26,0:10:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正阿耶最近迷上了比Jcube更好玩的游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.18,0:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以下是shell目前可参加的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.35,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最近在破解这个任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.40,0:10:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与飞船上的神秘人物接触？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.32,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Jungle群的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是阿耶没有加入的群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近这样的消息一直误传过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦  美咲咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会陪我一起上飞船的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用那个奇怪的称呼叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.41,0:11:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则就不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.20,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你愿意陪我去吗  美咲妹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.79,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  别总是这样黏着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.96,0:11:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见  你也会一起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.76,0:11:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干嘛要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.26,0:11:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我从来没跟女生单独外出过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  算我求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直这样瞪我  为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.32,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.95,0:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还在看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.67,0:12:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞船会在今晚路过这栋大楼上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.76,0:12:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在飞船底下启动这个叫“蜡烛”的APP
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.31,0:12:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞船就会接我们上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.81,0:12:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道飞船会通过这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Jungle上有任务提示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是数字啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.36,0:12:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿耶用自己写的程序分析了这串数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把结果排列到地图上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面到底写了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会显示出飞船的飞行路径
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大贝  你还挺厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要阿耶出手  小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈  什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说要到朋友家写作业吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.94,0:13:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说了  是妈妈没在听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.15,0:13:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说你跟大贝是什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.91,0:13:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来你们是有点像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接一下电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.71,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟我妈说要去一个叫美咲的女生家写作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.93,0:13:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果她说想跟你打声招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁是女生啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题  美咲你一定骗得过她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.19,0:13:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男子汉就放手一搏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  帮帮忙嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是穿帮了别怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.54,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  豁出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让你们见识什么叫男子汉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.21,0:14:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  让你们知道什么叫妩媚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.34,0:14:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸会呢  人家是八田美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.85,0:14:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的呢  人家正跟阿耶亲一起写作业呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦  妈妈也快回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.11,0:14:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会啦  怎么会麻烦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好哒  下次人家也会去你家玩的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.32,0:14:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的呢  再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.66,0:14:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这一辈子的女子力都用光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下满意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的危机解除了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.38,0:14:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了  真是精彩的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会再帮你第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见  连你都在笑我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能  猿比古居然笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是飞船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比预估时间来的更快  而且距离还更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能  坐标跟高度都正确输入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想重新计算吗  太没礼貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿耶的计算是不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.89,0:15:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在这情况已经出现误差了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.61,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能直接把数字输入进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是某种编码？还是质因数分解？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外行人有办法解析到如此地步吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该没有那么复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就类似解谜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对数字进行增减
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.71,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是不行吗  不然位数重组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这样行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.97,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0K  就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.18,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要以这规则转换成数字  再输入地图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子啊  伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛关掉地图啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的路径不是正确的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.53,0:16:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里等  是等不到飞船的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.33,0:16:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算点了“蜡烛”飞船也看不到这么远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里太冷了  我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.01,0:17:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去追追看嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都能看见飞船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经看见了就别放弃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是追得上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个也上车吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人骑一辆自行车？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.53,0:17:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧  反正她愿意当步兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿耶要当步兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人真的有够讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死都不愿意抱着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是  就算死了也别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.68,0:17:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩关系差就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.55,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可别摔下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这前面  继续前进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.39,0:18:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大艘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没赶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.37,0:18:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊  就我一个人一头热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.13,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能乘上飞船  会改变什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.14,0:19:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  说不定它能带我们到一个新地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.94,0:19:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像这里又愚蠢又无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.65,0:19:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是某个遥远又不一样的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.99,0:19:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样的世界吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.85,0:19:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.14,0:20:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的是伏见家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伏见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个感冒请假的人在做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.51,0:20:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田  你怎么来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.89,0:20:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师要我带讲义给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这房间好闷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开五分钟的窗户  你先盖上被子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.65,0:20:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家好像没人  你有吃东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.53,0:20:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人也有聒噪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.41,0:20:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我帮你煮个菜粥好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家里总有米  鸡蛋和酱油的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么愉快地决定了  厨房借我用用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.96,0:21:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就先睡一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.05,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我门就不关了  有事就叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随传随到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.31,0:21:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里还真没人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.36,0:21:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就他一个人感冒在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.15,0:21:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我口渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.03,0:21:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好  想喝什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.95,0:21:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡的葡萄汁君  果汁0％的那种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微碳酸的更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要求还挺多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.96,0:21:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0％不就是根本不含果汁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.17,0:21:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想喝就喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.14,0:21:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得附近有便利店的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.81,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零钱在客厅餐具橱上的盘子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.19,0:22:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.48,0:22:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.94,0:22:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.24,0:22:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  再帮我买个雪糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.24,0:22:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊  发烧了就会想吃点冰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.87,0:22:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我买淡的香草冰淇淋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.83,0:22:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还真喜欢淡的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.54,0:22:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.76,0:22:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.59,0:22:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了随传随到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.97,0:22:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还打算试几次啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.06,0:22:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  你不用一直喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心睡你的觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想叫你关窗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.95,0:22:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好  抱歉是我忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.46,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃  不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.75,0:23:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  要先打个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.88,0:23:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我在朋友家今天晚点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.74,0:23:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你谁啊  哪家的孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.91,0:23:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学生吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  醒醒啊小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.21,0:23:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰了  我是伏见的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.59,0:24:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟猿比古同班的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.72,0:24:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是猿比古在学校里的死党？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.23,0:24:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么小只  还以为是小学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.23,0:24:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是伏见的老爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.20,0:24:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是猿比古的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.78,0:24:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.28,0:24:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.95,0:24:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在问你名字  给我报全名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.21,0:24:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八美美咲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.71,0:24:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲？听起来像女人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.76,0:24:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.42,0:24:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在学校里肯定经常被嘲笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.72,0:24:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小学生最喜欢拿这个当梗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.35,0:24:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  还好啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.06,0:24:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我家的猴子就把死党一个人丢在这著吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.99,0:25:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古  快出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.78,0:25:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定听见我声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.45,0:25:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再躲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.46,0:25:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是再不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.71,0:25:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就往你新朋友的嘴里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.59,0:25:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞一只螳螂哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.40,0:25:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是轻而易举就把你吓出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.32,0:25:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田  你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.24,0:25:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我才刚子菜粥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.12,0:25:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且味道还不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.21,0:25:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.08,0:25:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这么体贴的朋友赶走  太过分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.92,0:26:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了烟花  一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.84,0:26:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过应该会被这雨打湿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.26,0:26:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像玩俄多斯轮盘一样  插在你朋友头上点火怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.81,0:26:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定运气好就点着一根了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:22.19,0:26:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:31.54,0:26:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了  生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.04,0:26:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在生气好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.00,0:26:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.55,0:26:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生气的猴子真是太好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.90,0:26:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.28,0:27:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重身体啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.49,0:27:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:06.61,0:27:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.66,0:27:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快进屋吧  会着凉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.71,0:27:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:19.79,0:27:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来探病…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.13,0:27:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候  不是应该说声谢谢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.43,0:27:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  下次你来我家玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.18,0:27:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我家有弟弟妹妹很吵就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.65,0:27:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  学校见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:01.33,0:28:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿比古
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.43,0:28:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一起玩吧
